data.description: Location, Location! Large lot on green belt, in New Braunfels! Spacious home located on a private court, with a large backyard and no neighbor behind! Large primary suite on the first floor features a garden tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. A true 4 bedroom plus an office and upstairs loft! Located in the fast growing area of New Braunfels. Close to I35, schools and shopping. This home is a must see!
